#%PAM-1.0

# Password authentication stack for qbar-lock (the typed-password unlock path).
#
# Fingerprint is NOT configured here: qbar-lock talks to fprintd over D-Bus
# directly (so it can run in parallel with the password and be cancelled cleanly),
# not through pam_fprintd. Nothing to add for fingerprint.
#
# Face unlock (Howdy) is a SEPARATE stack — see qbar-lock-face — selected with
# --face-pam-service qbar-lock-face.
auth include login
account include login
